ublic group of companies and vice chairman of mccannerickson worldgroup where he was the youngest member ever to join mccann’s board of directors  earlier in his career dowley ran momentum worldwide the event and experiential marketing unit of mccannerickson that was named the top event marketing and sales promotion company in the world by advertising age dowley’s work and his proficiency for developing partnerships have been recognized by several industry publications and numerous accolades  he has appeared on crain’s new york business’ prestigious “forty under ” list and was a threetime inductee to the same list in sports business journal  currently dowley is a member of the board of trustees of the united states ski and snowboard association and sits on the board of directors of allclear holdings a biometrics company the child mind institute he is a graduate of the college of wooster of which he is also a trustee team david moross david gubbay colbey arden linda marr steve gintowt michael lorelli advisor ray cosman mark dowley gavin forbes charles goldstuck robert kain andy laszlo charley moore harvey w schiller frank vuono christopher weil macandrews  forbes group llc k rating by brightscope getsearchtypedisplaynamesearchtype advisor funds firms k plans homek directorymacandrews  forbes group llc macandrews  forbes group llcform  data overviewplan componentsinvestmentsprovidersarticles  questions share print macandrews  forbes group llc  macandrews  forbes group llc saving macandrews  forbes group llc savings or cash option plan for employees form  data overviewplan componentsinvestmentsprovidersarticles  questions overview plan rating brightscope rating  lowest rating in peer group average rating in peer group highest rating in peer group  lowest in peer group  average in peer group  highest in peer group  plan description macandrews  forbes group llc savings or cash option plan for employees is a defined contribution plan with a profitsharing component and k f